title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 7PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 7PM” game were:
8-3-9-9
(eight, three, nine, nine)
